---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Why Watch Stories puts editorial context before the buying link.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <p class="kicker">Our point of view</p>
      <h1>A watch becomes meaningful before it becomes yours.</h1>
      <p class="intro">We tell the stories behind timepieces so choosing one feels considered, personal, and worth remembering.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="manifesto">
    <div class="container manifesto-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="kicker">Why we exist</p>
        <h2>Less catalogue.<br />More connection.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="copy">
        <p>A specification can describe a watch, but it cannot explain why it stays in your mind. We look at craft, place, design, heritage, and the life a watch was made to accompany.</p>
        <p>Only after that story do we offer a path to CreationWatches, where readers can check current price and availability.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="principles">
    <div class="principle dark"><span>01</span><h3>See the watch</h3><p>Every journey begins with form, proportion, material, and a first impression.</p></div>
    <div class="principle light"><span>02</span><h3>Understand its world</h3><p>History and context turn a product into an object with character.</p></div>
    <div class="principle green"><span>03</span><h3>Choose with clarity</h3><p>The buying link appears when the story has done its work.</p></div>
  </section>

  <section class="disclosure">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="kicker">Transparency</p>
      <h2>Independent stories, clearly disclosed links.</h2>
      <p>Some links point to CreationWatches. We may earn a commission when a reader purchases through them, at no extra cost to the reader.</p>
      <a href="/watches">Explore the watch collection <span>→</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .container { width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 2rem)); margin: 0 auto; }
  .kicker { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .about-hero { min-height: 720px; display: grid; align-items: end; color: #fff; background: #263a38; }
  .hero-inner { padding-bottom: 7rem; }
  .about-hero h1 { max-width: 900px; font-size: 5.2rem; line-height: 1; }
  .intro { max-width: 620px; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .manifesto { padding: 10rem 0; background: #f6f3ed; }
  .manifesto-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr; gap: 8rem; }
  .manifesto h2, .disclosure h2 { font-size: 4rem; line-height: 1.08; }
  .copy { display: grid; gap: 2rem; color: var(--color-subtle); font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.9; }
  .principles { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  .principle { min-height: 520px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: end; padding: 4rem; }
  .principle span { margin-bottom: auto; font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .18em; }
  .principle h3 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
  .principle p { margin-top: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .dark { color: #fff; background: #1d2927; }
  .light { background: #e8e1d6; }
  .green { color: #fff; background: #4d625b; }
  .disclosure { padding: 10rem 0; text-align: center; background: #fff; }
  .disclosure .container { max-width: 900px; }
  .disclosure > .container > p:not(.kicker) { max-width: 680px; margin: 2rem auto; color: var(--color-muted); }
  .disclosure a { display: inline-flex; gap: 1rem; padding-bottom: .4rem; border-bottom: 1px solid; text-decoration: none; font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .about-hero { min-height: 650px; }
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 3.3rem; }
    .manifesto-grid, .principles { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .manifesto { padding: 6rem 0; }
    .manifesto-grid { gap: 3rem; }
    .manifesto h2, .disclosure h2 { font-size: 2.7rem; }
    .principle { min-height: 420px; padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
